snippet.title: Finding Frankie Story Trailer - Future Games Show Spring Showcase 2025
snippet.description:
A gore-soaked story trailer for Finding Frankie brought us into the world of this spine-chilling parkour platformer, where you're taunted by a team of terrifying animatronics. It's coming to consoles on April 15.

https://www.youtube.com/@FutureGamesShow

#FutureGamesShow #FGS #findingfrankie 

Future Publishing uses the Epidemic Sound Library and Adobe Creative Cloud Generative AI features
